| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4471 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4b1529d0-57fc-5ae0-859d-bfa09cacc97e"
